---
title: "US40 — View / manage subscription"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Premium User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>SubscriptionScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>CancelSubscription / Resubscribe
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>SupabaseGateway
  A->>B: open Subscription
  B-->>A: status, renews-at, $9.99/mo (simulated)
  A->>B: tap Cancel
  B->>C: cancel()
  C->>G: update subscriptions.status=cancelled
  G-->>C: ok
  C-->>B: cancelled (access until period end)
  B-->>A: status updated
